external_knowledge:
- 'Telescoping Solution' refers to a specific solution used in the tests; 
- 'most devoted users' implies the users who accessed the tests the most; 
- 'masterminds' refers to the full names of the users; 
- 'speed of completion' is indicated by the average execution time of the tests.

- "speediest" refers to the tests with the shortest execution times; 
- "telescoping tests" refers to tests that utilize the 'Telescoping Solution';
- The ranking is determined by the execution times of the tests in ascending order.
